5.1.7. Accidental purchases: Once Customers installs and activates the eSIM bundle, it will be considered used. No refunds will be offered.
5.1.8. Incorrect charges: If the Customer reasonably and in good faith disputes an invoice or part of it, the Customer shall notify Firsty of such a dispute within twelve (12) days of receipt of the invoice, providing details of why the invoiced amount is incorrect and, if possible, how much the Customer considers due. (See details in section 4.2 CHARGES FOR USE under Terms and Conditions)
